		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />About the only thing that could cause the 2 button to be completely broken while everything else works is that button 2 slider being faulty...<br /><br />Clean it, bypass it (removing turbo), whatever you've got to do.  Once you fix that you should be working.

		

		</td>
